      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA FLYER (6) last start winner (30.54) at The Meadows who is building a strong winning record. Rates highly here and will go close. PAW SAKAKIBURA (4) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, holding on for a minor placing when second and beaten 2 lengths at this track over 350m in 19.48. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in the finish again. WINKING WILLIE (3) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a second place finish (19.17) there the start prior. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. The form out of last race has been strong. Has the ability to give this a shake. HAPPY AND NUMB (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.",
